reviewText: I just started collecting live concert DVDs.  This is one that I will watch time and again - professional, entertaining, humorous, worshipful, and good quality sound/video right in your living room.

My family (including husband, sons 10 and 6) loves and enjoys watching and singing to this DVD often. The music are very uplifting and God-honoring. It's fun to watch the three guys singing and see their love for the Lord. Simply wonderful!
Great inspiration and leadership sets the example of what it is really all about.  Awesome.  I loved it!
A fantastic DVD in excellent condition!
Awesome,  awesome,  awesome. Love this DVD!
Better than describe!! Completely new DVD!! I loved the concert of this singers! The best..!!
Listen to the lyrics closely and be prepared to be blessed. These are songs bound to be classics, if they are not already.
These guys have definitely matured vocally since many of these songs' original recordings. The entire DVD is filled with some of PC&D's best work ever. Highly recommended!
